sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Operator
    participant Job as LMEval Job Pod
    participant ConfigMap as ConfigMap<br/>/meta/job.json
    participant Secret as Model Auth Secret<br/>(volume mount)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Serving Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Operator,Job: Flow 1: Normal Benchmark Evaluation

    Operator->>Job: Creates Kubernetes Job<br/>(mounts ConfigMap + Secrets)
    Job->>ConfigMap: Read job specification<br/>Filesystem mount
    Job->>Secret: Resolve model credentials<br/>(API key, HF token, CA cert)

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Bearer Token
    Job->>HFHub: GET datasets, tokenizers<br/>HF_TOKEN (optional, for gated repos)
    HFHub-->>Job: Benchmark datasets + configs

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: LOADING_DATA<br/>Bearer Token

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING_EVALUATION<br/>Bearer Token

    loop Batched completions (num_concurrent ≤ 128)
        Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)
        Model-->>Job: Completion response
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>Bearer Token

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS<br/>Bearer Token
    Job->>OCI: Push evaluation results as OCI artifact<br/>Registry credentials
    OCI-->>Job: Push confirmation

    Job->>MLflow: POST evaluation metrics + run metadata<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflow-->>Job: Log confirmation

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETED + results<br/>Bearer Token

    Note over Job,Model: Flow 2: Offline / Air-Gapped Evaluation

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Operator->>Job: Creates Kubernetes Job<br/>(with /test_data volume)
        Job->>ConfigMap: Read job specification<br/>Filesystem mount
        Job->>Secret: Resolve model credentials

        Note over Job: Auto-detect offline mode:<br/>tokenizer found under /test_data<br/>Sets HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1 + 5 more env vars

        Job->>Job: Load datasets + tokenizer<br/>from /test_data (local filesystem)

        loop Batched completions
            Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)
            Model-->>Job: Completion response
        end

        Note over Job,HFHub: No outbound calls to HuggingFace Hub
    end
